  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.classes.X3SHuud5tqrgznjP]{Stippling Shades}</p><p>Your spells are veiled and gain the illusion trait. If your spells require a spell attack, compare the attack roll to a creature's Perception DC. If they require a saving throw, targeted creatures need to make a Seek check before rolling their saving throw.</p><p>On a failure to disbelieve the illusion, your target takes a -2 status penalty to their AC or saving throw against the spell. If they critically succeed, they gain a +1 status bonus instead. At 8th rank, they take a -1 status penalty even if they succeed.</p>"
